name: Dockerignore
content:
# Ignore version control
.git
.gitignore

# Ignore dependencies
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Ignore build outputs
dist/
coverage/

# Ignore environment files
.env
.env.*

# Ignore logs
*.log
logs/

# Ignore IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Ignore OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Ignore test files
*.test.js
*.spec.js
__tests__/

# Ignore temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp
.cache/
